attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: This impeccable 3 bed, 2 bath home offers the pinnacle of modern luxury. The open-concept living area is bathed in natural light, highlighted by expansive windows and a chef's kitchen featuring a striking 10 ft island, top-tier Sub Zero and Wolf appliances, a wet bar, and a wine refrigerator. Elegant coffered ceilings, hardwood floors, and a private balcony with gas line. The spacious primary suite is a true retreat, complete with a large walk-in closet and a spa-like en-suite bath featuring a double vanity, soaking tub, and steam shower. Two additional generously sized bedrooms provide ample space and flexibility. Both oversized bathrooms showcase gorgeous stone countertops, custom tiling, and designer fixtures. Additional highlights include a dedicated laundry/storage room, brand new hot water heater, and 2 full size tandem parking spaces in heated garage. Residents also enjoy access to a spacious common roof deck and yard space. Walk to M Street park, shops & restaurants!
